<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-cn">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>404 - 页面未找到</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f5f6fa;
            font-family: "微软雅黑", Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 100px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .code {
            font-size: 72px;
            color: #ff9800;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .msg {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            background: #409eff;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        a:hover {
            background: #66b1ff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="code">404</div>
        <div class="msg">抱歉，您访问的页面不存在！</div>
        <a href="/">返回首页</a>
    </div>
</body>